overhanging clouds.

00:17:10.670 --> 00:17:12.470 align:middle line:84%
And I turned and
looked back down

00:17:12.470 --> 00:17:15.980 align:middle line:84%
to see this boat was now
searching frantically to try

00:17:15.980 --> 00:17:19.099 align:middle line:90%
