00:18:37.600 --> 00:18:41.730 align:middle line:84%
had on everybody
I interacted with.

00:18:41.730 --> 00:18:45.090 align:middle line:84%
From this place of
seeing all this,

00:18:45.090 --> 00:18:47.940 align:middle line:84%
my body, meanwhile,
