00:18:47.940 --> 00:18:53.010 align:middle line:84%
with the most profound
love, forgiveness, healing.

00:18:53.010 --> 00:18:58.140 align:middle line:84%
And from there it was as if I
was launched out into the God's

00:18:58.140 --> 00:19:01.210 align:middle line:90%
own internet, if you will.

00:19:01.210 --> 00:19:03.960 align:middle line:90%
From there I was resuscitated.

00:19:03.960 --> 00:19:05.880 align:middle line:84%
Meanwhile, I'd been
pulled out of the water.

00:19:05.880 --> 00:19:07.350 align:middle line:84%
I was being given
mouth to mouth.

00:19:07.350 --> 00:19:11.600 align:middle line:84%
I was coughing up water, and
