near-death experience,

00:19:16.670 --> 00:19:20.060 align:middle line:84%
for about three days, there
was this profound awareness

00:19:20.060 --> 00:19:24.900 align:middle line:84%
within my body that I was
a soul inhabiting my body.

00:19:24.900 --> 00:19:27.610 align:middle line:84%
But after about three
days that faded,

00:19:27.610 --> 00:19:30.980 align:middle line:90%
and I became normal again.

00:19:30.980 --> 00:19:35.020 align:middle line:84%
So it took me a long
time to fully integrate.

00:19:35.020 --> 00:19:36.940 align:middle line:84%
And there was times
when I wondered

00:19:36.940 --> 00:19:38.230 align:middle line:90%
had I ever been changed?

00:19:38.230 --> 00:19:40.240 align:middle line:90%
Was this really real?

00:19:40.240 --> 00:19:44.680 align:middle line:84%
But there was a simple guiding
principle that the voice of God

00:19:44.680 --> 00:19:47.080 align:middle line:84%
had spoken so
clearly to me, which

00:19:47.080 --> 00:19:49.480 align:middle line:84%
was an answer to a prayer
I'd had as a child,

00:19:49.480 --> 00:19:52.160 align:middle line:84%
wanting to change the
world as so many of us do,

00:19:52.160 --> 00:19:54.640 align:middle line:84%
wanting to be of
service to the world.

00:19:54.640 --> 00:19:56.650 align:middle line:90%
And the message was simple.

00:19:56.650 --> 00:20:00.730 align:middle line:84%
If you want to heal the world,
first connect to yourself.

00:20:00.730 --> 00:20:03.640 align:middle line:90%
Really know yourself.

00:20:03.640 --> 00:20:06.640 align:middle line:90%
And that's a big job.

00:20:06.640 --> 00:20:10.120 align:middle line:84%
By connecting to yourself you
bring healing to yourself.

00:20:10.120 --> 00:20:13.900 align:middle line:84%
From there you connect
to your family.

00:20:13.900 --> 00:20:15.860 align:middle line:84%
I had estranged
myself from my family.

00:20:15.860 --> 00:20:20.020 align:middle line:84%
So I returned to my family
to make those connections.

00:20:20.020 --> 00:20:22.540 align:middle line:84%
From there, connect
to the community.

00:20:22.540 --> 00:20:24.010 align:middle line:90%
I wasn't part of any community.

00:20:24.010 --> 00:20:25.600 align:middle line:84%
I was anonymous
in New York City.

00:20:25.600 --> 00:20:30.820 align:middle line:84%
So I returned to my
hometown, my family,

00:20:30.820 --> 00:20:35.500 align:middle line:84%
doing work in the community,
real service work.

00:20:35.500 --> 00:20:38.620 align:middle line:84%
And from there, you can
then make a connection

00:20:38.620 --> 00:20:40.150 align:middle line:84%
with your nation,
and from there you

00:20:40.150 --> 00:20:42.530 align:middle line:90%
can affect healing the world.

00:20:42.530 --> 00:20:45.460 align:middle line:84%
But ultimately it's a spiral
that goes around and around

00:20:45.460 --> 00:20:48.280 align:middle line:84%
and always returns you to a
deeper level of connecting

00:20:48.280 --> 00:20:50.710 align:middle line:90%
to yourself, knowing yourself.

00:20:50.710 --> 00:20:53.440 align:middle line:84%
So I came to know
myself fairly well,

00:20:53.440 --> 00:20:55.810 align:middle line:84%
got very involved in
my family and witnessed

00:20:55.810 --> 00:20:59.870 align:middle line:84%
some amazing transformations
within my family dynamics.

00:20:59.870 --> 00:21:03.220 align:middle line:84%
I became very involved in
unity work in my community.

00:21:03.220 --> 00:21:06.490 align:middle line:84%
And then the call came, the
realization that the time was

00:21:06.490 --> 00:21:08.140 align:middle line:90%
now to walk across the country.

00:21:08.140 --> 00:21:11.930 align:middle line:84%
That was my connecting
to the nation.

00:21:11.930 --> 00:21:14.400 align:middle line:84%
I walked from Ocean City,
Maryland to San Francisco,

00:21:14.400 --> 00:21:22.770 align:middle line:84%
California across Route 50
as a statement for unity,

00:21:22.770 --> 00:21:26.310 align:middle line:84%
as a testimony to the oneness
that is true between all of us.

00:21:26.310 --> 00:21:29.230 align:middle line:90%


00:21:29.230 --> 00:21:31.530 align:middle line:84%
There is an
interconnectedness that

00:21:31.530 --> 00:21:34.830 align:middle line:84%
was so apparent in my
near-death experience that

00:21:34.830 --> 00:21:37.230 align:middle line:90%
can be seen if only you look.

00:21:37.230 --> 00:21:39.120 align:middle line:90%
It's right there.

00:21:39.120 --> 00:21:42.570 align:middle line:84%
It's the amazing grace
that the song sings about.

00:21:42.570 --> 00:21:47.380 align:middle line:84%
It's the recognition
that we are all one,

00:21:47.380 --> 00:21:49.866 align:middle line:90%
and we're in this together.

00:21:49.866 --> 00:21:51.240 align:middle line:84%
But at the end of
all that, I was

00:21:51.240 --> 00:21:57.570 align:middle line:84%
left feeling more deeply
aware of levels within myself

00:21:57.570 --> 00:22:01.230 align:middle line:90%
that I was not yet aware of.

00:22:01.230 --> 00:22:06.480 align:middle line:84%
Healing the world starts
with healing yourself.

00:22:06.480 --> 00:22:10.890 align:middle line:84%
This unity consciousness
is something that

00:22:10.890 --> 00:22:14.580 align:middle line:90%
has to be held within first.

00:22:14.580 --> 00:22:20.220 align:middle line:84%
The message that love your
brother as you love yourself,

00:22:20.220 --> 00:22:22.780 align:middle line:84%
or love others as
you love yourself,

00:22:22.780 --> 00:22:25.200 align:middle line:84%
you have to ask yourself,
do you love yourself?

00:22:25.200 --> 00:22:28.740 align:middle line:84%
Because many of us do,
in fact, love others

00:22:28.740 --> 00:22:29.640 align:middle line:90%
as we love ourselves.

00:22:29.640 --> 00:22:32.050 align:middle line:84%
The truth is we
loathe ourselves.

00:22:32.050 --> 00:22:36.420 align:middle line:84%
So this simple process,
being able to lift myself up

00:22:36.420 --> 00:22:40.320 align:middle line:84%
from the despair and the
confusions of any given moment

00:22:40.320 --> 00:22:42.510 align:middle line:84%
back to that larger
picture perspective

00:22:42.510 --> 00:22:44.910 align:middle line:84%
from the near-death
experience, combined

00:22:44.910 --> 00:22:49.050 align:middle line:84%
with this simple guidance of
connecting again and again,

00:22:49.050 --> 00:22:52.110 align:middle line:84%
is what has sustained
me and moved me forward

00:22:52.110 --> 00:22:54.454 align:middle line:90%
for the last 16 years.

